org.springframework.test.web.client.RequestExpectationManager

  • 使用RequestExpectationManager的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    org.springframework.test.web.client
    Contains client-side REST testing support.

    • org.springframework.test.web.client中RequestExpectationManager的使用

      实现RequestExpectationManager的org.springframework.test.web.client中的类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  AbstractRequestExpectationManager
      Base class for RequestExpectationManager implementations responsible for storing expectations and actual requests, and checking for unsatisfied expectations at the end.
      class  SimpleRequestExpectationManager
      Simple RequestExpectationManager that matches requests to expectations sequentially, i.e. in the order of declaration of expectations.
      class  UnorderedRequestExpectationManager
      RequestExpectationManager that matches requests to expectations regardless of the order of declaration of expected requests.
      参数类型为RequestExpectationManager的org.springframework.test.web.client中的方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      MockRestServiceServer MockRestServiceServer.MockRestServiceServerBuilder.build(RequestExpectationManager manager)
      An overloaded build alternative that accepts a custom RequestExpectationManager.
